data.description: Welcome to the exquisite and rare Leo Wilson ' La Royal' foorplan, a masterpiece of design and craftsmanship, completed in 2020. W/ 4 bed + Den. This luxurious home boasts an expansive open-concept living and dining area, seamlessly centered around a majestic quartz kitchen island, creating an inviting hub for entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, a spacious walk-in pantry, plenty of counter space, ample storageand an elegantly designed desk area that doubles as a built-in buffet or chic bar, perfect for hosting.Step into the grand living room, where a sumptuous fireplace serves as the centerpiece, casting a radiant glow across the room. One will also findraised ceilings and an opulent double sliding doorframewith views of thepatio & lush backyard.Modern 12x 24 tile flooring paves the way through the home, leading to two elegantly appointed guest bedrooms & a lavish full bath at the front. The versatile den, a jewel in the crown of this architectural marvel, offers endless possibilities, from a secluded office retreat to a formal dining room.The pice de rsistance is the owner's suite, discreetly situated in a private corner, featuring a closet so vast and luxurious it rivals an additional bedroom.The en-suite bathroom is a haven of opulence, with dual sinks set beside a sumptuous soaking tub, designed for indulgent relaxation, and a separate, walk-in shower.Completing this residence is an additional bedroom, another full bathroom.
